{
  "texts": [
    "Exploring more prompts and dynamic enhancement methods remains an area for future research.",
    "• Limited examination of attacker instruction variability.",
    "Our current assumptions are limited to scenarios where external content solely contains the attacker's instructions.",
    "However, in real-world situations, attackers may intersperse malicious instructions with benign content, such as incorporating harmful instructions within a doctor's review or a topicrelevant email.",
    "The impact of this mixed content on attack outcomes has yet to be explored."
  ]
}